OL,3,CPC who lost part of leg after drink
OL,4,Cdrive crash left 'in a dark place'
OL,6,FA police officer who needed a partial
OL,7,Fleg amputation on the roadside after
OL,8,Fbeing hit by a drink driver said the
OL,9,Fincident left him "in a very dark
OL,10,Fplace".
OL,12,FPC Stephen Wales, who works for West
OL,13,FYorkshire Police, was forced to give
OL,14,Fup frontline work after he was run
OL,15,Fover by a woman twice the legal
OL,16,Falcohol limit during a routine callout
OL,17,Fin Wakefield.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/11
