OL,3,CPC who lost part of leg after drink
OL,4,Cdrive crash left 'in a dark place'
OL,6,FThe father-of-two said: "It's been
OL,7,Freally challenging to the point some
OL,8,Fdays where I didn't think I'd ever
OL,9,Frecover from it.
OL,11,F"I used to sit and sob and cry to my
OL,12,Fpartner and kids, and worry about my
OL,13,Fkids health because it affected them
OL,14,Fmassively.
OL,16,F"My girls thought they'd never see
OL,17,Ftheir dad again. It put me in a very
OL,18,Fvery dark place. I was up in the night
OL,19,Fcrying, sobbing, saying, how am I
OL,20,Fgoing to get through this?."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
