OL,6,FPC Wales was responding to another
OL,7,Fincident when the collision happened
OL,8,Fin 2021.
OL,10,FHe said he had got out of his police
OL,11,Fvan when he was sent "hurtling through
OL,12,Fthe air".
OL,14,F"I landed straight on my feet and my
OL,15,Flegs snapped from beneath me," he said.
OL,17,F"It was surreal. It felt fast but also
OL,18,Fslow motion. You know when you see war
OL,19,Ffilms and you hear that ringing noise
OL,20,F- it was like that."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/11
