OL,3,CPC who lost part of leg after drink
OL,4,Cdrive crash left 'in a dark place'
OL,6,FTwo members of the public were also
OL,7,Fhit by the car and had to have leg
OL,8,Famputations.
OL,10,FA woman was later jailed for three
OL,11,Fyears and eight months.
OL,13,FPC Wales has since undergone seven
OL,14,Foperations to save his legs, spending
OL,15,Falmost 40 hours under the knife.
OL,17,FAfter being told by doctors he may
OL,18,Fnever walk again, he had intensive
OL,19,Frehabilitation and now walks with the
OL,20,Fhelp of specially designed aids.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/11
