OL,6,FBut he has been left struggling to
OL,7,Fcope with the psychological impact.
OL,9,F"I've had quite a lot of therapy, CBT
OL,10,Ftherapy, which has been a massive help
OL,11,F- it's pulled me through. I think just
OL,12,Ftalking about it has helped," he said.
OL,14,F"I can openly admit today that I could
OL,15,Fhave quite easily said I've had enough
OL,16,Fbut I didn't want to give in."
OL,18,FThe incident came just a year after PC
OL,19,FWales was faced with an attacker who
OL,20,Fhad just stabbed a man 13 times.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/11
