OL,6,FIn an incident caught on bodycam, the
OL,7,Fman, who was still armed, lunged at PC
OL,8,FWales and a trainee officer when they
OL,9,Fresponded to the incident in
OL,10,FPontefract.
OL,12,FHe said: "At that moment my daughters'
OL,13,Ffaces just flashed in my eyes.
OL,15,F"I shot him with a taser and it had no
OL,16,Fimpact. It sort of charged him up and
OL,17,Fhe just lunged at me with the knife
OL,18,Ftrying to attack me in the neck.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/11
