OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F366A1738869975
OL,3,CPC who lost part of leg after drink
OL,4,Cdrive crash left 'in a dark place'
OL,6,F"He was just so overpowering and so
OL,7,Fstrong. I can't believe we managed to
OL,8,Fescape without a scratch.
OL,10,F"I never expected to face a scenario
OL,11,Flike that as a frontline police
OL,12,Fofficer. That's something you see in
OL,13,Fthe movies, not a single crew officer
OL,14,Fwith just a taser and a trainee. You
OL,15,Fdon't expect that level of violence."
OL,17,FAmong other incidents during PC Wales'
OL,18,F14-year career was dealing with the
OL,19,Fdeath of a three-year-old girl.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
