OL,4,Cdrive crash left 'in a dark place'
OL,6,FHe said: "That had a massive impact on
OL,7,Fme mentally. I went home sobbing my
OL,8,Fheart out and had a bit of a breakdown
OL,9,Fand had to have therapy.
OL,11,F"The things you face on a day to day
OL,12,Fbasis, they're just unreal compared to
OL,13,Fwhat a member of the public does in a
OL,14,Flifetime. You're faced with such
OL,15,Ftraumatic incidents from the very
OL,16,Ftrivial to the most extreme.
OL,18,F"It's not so much when you're at work,
OL,19,Fit's when you get home and start to
OL,20,Fdwell on it and think 'what if?'"
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/11
