OL,6,FPC Wales had to give up his career as
OL,7,Fa frontline officer and now works from
OL,8,Fhome in an administrative role for the
OL,9,Fforce.
OL,11,FHe spoke about the mental health
OL,12,Fimpact of police work after an ITV
OL,13,FCalendar investigation found that
OL,14,Fofficers in Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,15,Ftook about 60,000 days off last year
OL,16,Fdue to stress.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
