OL,6,FPC Wales said: "It's been a massive
OL,7,Fchange and it still impacts me. It's
OL,8,Fhard mentally just being sat in an
OL,9,Foffice job, and it's hard for me
OL,10,Fphysically not being moving.
OL,12,F"But the new role is fulfilling and I
OL,13,Fdo feel like I make a difference
OL,14,Fwithin the policing world. It's
OL,15,Fsatisfying knowing I can still make a
OL,16,Fbit of a difference to the community
OL,17,Fout there."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/11
