OL,6,FCraig Nicholls, chair of West
OL,7,FYorkshire Police Federation, said:
OL,8,F"Stephen's story is not uncommon -
OL,9,Ffrontline policing is incredibly
OL,10,Fdangerous, from going to the scene of
OL,11,Fa road traffic collision, going to a
OL,12,Fhouse fire and dragging people out,
OL,13,Fgoing to a shooting, giving first aid
OL,14,Fto adults and children.
OL,16,F"We have a finite budget and people
OL,17,Ftry their very best to work with that
OL,18,Fbudget but sometimes it's simply not
OL,19,Fenough. With the cuts, there are
OL,20,Fgenuine consequences."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/11
